For the 2001/02 marketing year:
(a) the minimum price referred to in Article 6b of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 for unprocessed dried figs shall be EUR 878,86 per tonne net ex-producer's premises;
(b) the production aid referred to in Article 6c of that Regulation for dried figs shall be EUR 286,30 per tonne net.
